video.title: Survivor
video.synopsis: In this long-running reality competition series, players battle the elements and each other as they vie for $1 million and the title of Sole Survivor.

episodes.synopsis: Ten "Survivor" superfans arrive in Micronesia, where a surprise awaits: They're about to face off against 10 favorite players from previous seasons.
episodes.title: You Guys Are Dumber Than You Look

episodes.synopsis: Four flirtatious Favorites form a power-couple alliance. After a rough start, three outsiders on the Fans tribe earn some respect.
episodes.title: The Sounds Of Jungle Love

episodes.synopsis: The tribes compete in a full-contact battle during the reward challenge. Torn between two alliances, one player lands in a powerful position.
episodes.title: I Should Be Carried On The Chariot-Type Thing

episodes.synopsis: The Fans lose patience with a weak tribe mate, while a sick castaway fights to stay in the game. One player creates a fake immunity idol.
episodes.title: That's A Baked, Barbecued and Fried

episodes.synopsis: A tribe swap shakes up the game, mixing Fans and Favorites. After an intense reward challenge, several contestants return to camp with injuries.
episodes.title: He's A Ball Of Goo

episodes.synopsis: A player's injury worsens. While one castaway relaxes on Exile Island, another searches high and low for an immunity idol.
episodes.title: It Hit Everyone Pretty Hard

episodes.synopsis: A Favorite takes an eager Fan under his wing, threatening existing alliances. Homesickness hits one of the other Fans hard.
episodes.title: Like A Wide-Eyed Kid In A Candy Store

episodes.synopsis: A few of the women devise a plan to target the strong men. Alone and isolated, one player takes desperate measures to stay in the game.
episodes.title: A Lost Little Puppy

episodes.synopsis: Allies reunite after the merge, and the first individual immunity challenge forces the castaways to stay calm under pressure.
episodes.title: I'm In Such A Hot Pickle

episodes.synopsis: At a grueling immunity challenge, Jeff tempts the players with food, and one castaway considers making a sacrifice for the tribe.
episodes.title: I Promise

episodes.synopsis: The castaways bid on food items at the auction, and one player gets sent to Exile Island, where a new hidden immunity idol awaits.
episodes.title: I'm Ruthless...and Have A Smile On My Face

episodes.synopsis: Two contestants suffer injuries. At the reward challenge, the castaways compete to spend an afternoon with their loved ones.
episodes.title: I'm Gonna Fix Her

episodes.synopsis: With only five castaways left, members of an alliance put their powers of persuasion to the test, trying to manipulate another player.
episodes.title: If It Smells Like A Rat, Give It Cheese

episodes.synopsis: With $1 million on the line, the final contestants plead their cases to a jury of Fans and Favorites.
episodes.title: Stir The Pot

episodes.synopsis: Jeff reveals the winner and fan favorite as the castaways reunite to look back on the season.
episodes.title: The Reunion Show

episodes.synopsis: The castaways learn they've been divided into tribes of underdogs and overachievers as the Davids take on the Goliaths in the first challenge.
episodes.title: Appearances Are Deceiving

episodes.synopsis: Endless rain leaves both tribes struggling. A budding showmance could make targets out of two Goliaths, while the Davids debate their next move.
episodes.title: The Chicken Has Flown the Coop

episodes.synopsis: Two brainy Davids forge a friendship, a paranoid Goliath calls a tribe meeting, and a competitor gets injured during the challenge.
episodes.title: I Am Goliath Strong

episodes.synopsis: After a tribe swap, castaways from the David and Goliath tribes must learn to work together. A riddle awaits one player on Exile Island.
episodes.title: Time to Bring About the Charmpocalypse

episodes.synopsis: One castaway has to scramble after being on the wrong side of the vote, and another turbulent storm puts a sudden halt to the game.
episodes.title: Jackets and Eggs

episodes.synopsis: The lines between former Davids and Goliaths blur, shaking up old alliances. Castaways on one tribe clash over conditions at camp.
episodes.title: Aren't Brochachos Just Adorable?

episodes.synopsis: At the merge, news of a blindside stirs up distrust. Players angle to build new alliances, and anything could happen as targets keep shifting.
episodes.title: There's Gonna Be Tears Shed

episodes.synopsis: One castaway must do damage control after being called out by the tribe. A stressful immunity challenge tests the competitors' balance.
episodes.title: You Get What You Give

episodes.synopsis: Allies weigh whether to stay Goliath strong or make a big move. The Davids wake up at dawn to search for an advantage.
episodes.title: Breadth-First Search

episodes.synopsis: The winners of the reward challenge receive letters from home. Then, contestants decide whether to eat or compete in an epic immunity challenge.
episodes.title: Tribal Lines Are Blurred: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: A castaway lets his guard down during a reward. At the immunity challenge, a player negotiates with Jeff to get more food for the tribe.
episodes.title: Tribal Lines Are Blurred: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Emotions run high as the castaways compete for a visit with their loved ones. A player is torn between strategy and friendship.
episodes.title: So Smart They're Dumb

episodes.synopsis: A player creates a fake immunity idol. Two allies strategize during a reward challenge outing. A castaway weighs whether to take a gamble.
episodes.title: Are You Feeling Lucky?

episodes.synopsis: The final six competitors scramble to find a hidden idol, then race to solve a massive puzzle with immunity on the line.
episodes.title: With Great Power Comes Great Responsibility: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Two players compete in a fire-making challenge. The final castaways face the jury, and Jeff reveals the winner at the live reunion.
episodes.title: With Great Power Comes Great Responsibility: Part 2
